      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "When Maintaining a Healthy Office Environment: A Guide for GPD Staff\n\nTo foster a positive work environment, it's essential to strike a balance between being approachable and maintaining personal boundaries. Start by practicing emotional intelligence: actively listen to colleagues, ask open-ended questions, and focus on finding solutions rather than placing blame. Establish clear limits on personal discussions and sensitive topics at work, politely redirecting conversations to maintain productivity. By striking this balance, you'll create an environment where everyone feels valued, supported, and respectful of others' space.",
